    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she is a total dream! This beauty is in truly spectacular shape; I\u2019ve babied it from day one, so it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom. Not a scratch to be found, and it still has that fresh, clean feel inside. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin, you seriously won't find one in better condition!",
