    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1995 Porsche 911 Carrera, showcasing the pinnacle of air-cooled engineering. The 3.6L M64 boxer engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders, delivering linear power through a precise G50/20 six-speed manual gearbox and a factory-optional limited-slip differential. The LSA (Lightweight-Stable-Agile) multi-link rear suspension remains tight, providing exceptional kinematic toe control and cornering poise. This vehicle features a meticulously maintained dry-sump oiling system with zero seepage and a pristine underbody. With its factory-spec Brembo braking system and a perfectly balanced rotating assembly, this 993 offers a visceral, analog driving experience in an unblemished, showroom-quality state.",
      "price": 49500.0,
