      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule. This vehicle is in showroom condition, featuring a deep, mirror-like exterior finish completely free of chips or swirls. Inside, the cabin remains pristine, retaining its original scent with leather upholstery that shows no signs of wear and buttons that feel crisp and new. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; it has been fastidiously maintained with a full-service history from authorized technicians, ensuring it drives with the same precision and smoothness as the day it was first delivered. From the spotless engine bay to the unblemished alloy wheels, every detail has been preserved for the most demanding collector.",
