    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it basically still has that new-car smell. I've babied it since day one, and it's been garage-kept and hand-washed only. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. You won't find one cleaner than this! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
